        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 17–22. SEM micrographs of Tyrrhenoleuctra sp. (Rio Andila, Estrema Dura, Spain) male structures. 17. Male terminalia, caudodorsal. 18. Male epiproct and paraprocts dorsal. 19. Male epiproct and paraprocts, dorsolateral. 20. Epiproct, lateral. 21. Epiproct and paraprocts, dorsoapical. 22. Vesicle, ventral. (ce = cercus; ep = epiproct; pp = paraprocts; ve = vesicle)" ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4753131/files/figure.png" .

